課程概述 Course Description
       1. Crystal structure 2. Crystal bonding 3. Defects 4. Mechanical properties 5. Failure 6.Metals, Ceramics 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    1. Understand fundamental metallurgical phenomena
2. Identify the compositions and properties of commercial alloys
3. Understand principles of metal fabrication
4. Illustrate different types of materials used in engineering designs and their relationship between structure and properties    

