	    1. Understand fundamental metallurgical phenomena
2. Identify the compositions and properties of commercial alloys
3. Understand principles of metal fabrication
4. Illustrate different types of materials used in engineering designs and their relationship between structure and properties    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Atomic Structure and Crystal Bonding2Atomic Structure and Crystal Bonding3Crystal Structure of Metals4Crystal Structure of Metals5Crystal Defects6Crystal Defects7Vacancies8Vacancies9Mechanical Properties of Metals10Mechanical Properties of Metals11Midterm exam12Dislocations, Plastic Deformation and Strengthening Mechanisms13Dislocations, Plastic Deformation and Strengthening Mechanisms14Failure of Materials15Failure of Materials16Ceramics and Glasses-Bonding and Structure, Properties and Processing17Ceramics and Glasses-Bonding and Structure, Properties and Processing18Final exam 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


