材料科學導論一



















ESS2500 Introduction to Materials Science I, 材料科學導論一










Course Description:
Atomic Structure, Crystal Structure, Defects, Deformation, Phase 
            Diagram and Phase Transformation; Emphasizing on the principle of basic 
            materials science, and the relation between the microstructure and the 
            materials properties (mechanical properties as an example).




課程說明：
            原子結構與晶體結構、晶體缺陷、材料機械性質、相圖與相變化; 
            本課程著重於
            基礎材料科學觀念之建立及材料微結構與材料性質關係之原理(以機械性質為例).












